premise_source_doc_sentence: Mark Bomback  (  born August 29 , 1971  )  is an American screenwriter , originally from New Rochelle , New York .
Bomback is a graduate of Wesleyan University , where he studied English Literature and Film Studies .
Dawn of the Planet of the Apes is a 2014 American science fiction film directed by Matt Reeves and written by Mark Bomback , Rick Jaffa and Amanda Silver .
Deception is a 2008 American crime thriller film directed by Marcel Langenegger and written by Mark Bomback .

Hugh Jackman reprises his role from previous films as the title character , with James Mangold directing a screenplay written by Scott Frank and Mark Bomback , based on the 1982 limited series Wolverine by Chris Claremont and Frank Miller .
